original_title: Brooklyn: Village Rd. N. - Lake St.
text:
Village Road North, south side, opposite Lake Street, showing the house occupied by J.S. Van Cleet in 1873? which is still standing in 1929, and to the left of which, partially seen, is No. 28; in the background, is a section of P.S. No. 95.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
